our head. Also like the EarPods, the Pixel Buds rest on your ear rather than create a firm seal in your ear canal, and I should point out that the earbud itself is quite big, not good for teeny ears. The resultant sound is crisp but surprisingly one-dimensional. The vocals on &ldquo;Ready for the Floor&rdquo; by Hot Chip come through cleanly, but the whole song sounds limp, since the Pixel Buds produce so little bass. &ldquo;Take Me Home, Country Roads&rdquo; by John Denver sounds terrific, although that song always sounds great to me.<br />\n<br />\n拎無線耳機同有線耳機比 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/29.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"40e699a259297789c4e33a049c60becfc5c89028","tid":469421,"uid":1557,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-15T16:14:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://gizmodo.com/googles-pixel-buds-arent-even-close-to-being-good-1820411288\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgizmodo.com%2Fgoogles-pixel-buds-arent-even-close-to-being-good-1820411288&d=dr%2BBXWo2Qwm1iMWF6fO1pcPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=adcc82e8\" target=\"_blank\">https://gizmodo.com/googles-pixel-buds-arent-even-close-to-being-good-1820411288</a><br />\n睇完篇文真係膠都廢事比<br />\n1. not true wireless -&gt; 其實有好多人prefer 有條線係中間  只可以話百貨應百客  你買之前已經知有條線  咁都有得屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n2. 其他電話用唔到full function, 得pixel 先支援到all function. -&gt; 你會唔會屌AirPods 唔支援其他電話 (用到但唔識自動配對), 人地叫Pixel Buds唔係Android Buds<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n3. 比音質果陣仲好笑  拎有線既EarPods 黎比  你要比都拎返AirPods黎比啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/